∀ {D : Type u_1} [inst : TopologicalSpace D] [inst_1 : BoundedSpace D] [inst_2 : ComplexManifold ℂ D]
  (f : D → ℂ) (γ : Path D), HolomorphicOn ℂ f D → Path.isLoop γ → ∮ z in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E]
  (f : ℂ → E) {γ : ℂ → ℂ} (hγ : IsClosedPath γ),
  (∀ z, HolomorphicAt ℂ f z) → (∮ z in hγ, f z) = 0

∀ {U : Type u_1} [inst : TopologicalSpace U] [inst_1 : ComplexManifold U]
  {f : U → ℂ} [inst_2 : IsHolomorphic f] {γ : Path U}, 
  Path.IsClosed γ → ∮ (z : U) in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {M : Type u_2} [inst_2 : TopologicalSpace M]
  [inst_3 : ChartedSpace ℂ M] [inst_4 : SmoothManifoldWithCorners (ModelWithCorners.self ℂ) M]
  {f : M → E}, IsHolomorphic f → ∀ (γ : Loop M), ∮ (z : M) in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Path ℂ),
  IsClosedPath γ → HolomorphicOn ℂ f (γ.image) → ∮ z in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : ℂ → ℂ) (hγ : IsClosed γ),
  (∀ z, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {γ : ℂ → E} {c : ℂ},
  IsClosed γ → (∀ (z : ℂ), DifferentiableAt ℂ γ z) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, γ z) = 0

∀ {Ω : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup Ω] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ Ω] {γ : ℂ → Ω} (f : Ω → ℂ),
  IsHolomorphic f → IsClosedPath γ → ∮ (z : Ω) in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : ℂ → ℂ} {s : Set ℂ},
  (∀ z ∈ s, DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → Path.IsLoop γ → (∮ z in s, f z) = 0
